Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.43,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は悲しく笑い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:53.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}僕はかける言葉もなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:56.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}景色は滲む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}始まればいずれ終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:02.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}綺麗事などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:05.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}せめて君を温めたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:15.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ほんの少しの時間を与えて　神様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:27.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}晨曦的光芒太過耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:33.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人不禁想要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:39.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坦露自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:44.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}任憑此身沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:47.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你握緊冰冷的十指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}臉上是悲切的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:53.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我無言以對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:56.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只有視野漸漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不需言語粉飾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:02.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}有始必定有終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:05.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}唯願能將你溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:15.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}神啊 請給我一點時間
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff1,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見 你會記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕會就這樣習慣了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得自己好像會變成別的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家其實都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,始終不變這種事或許沒有人能夠做到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我們確實活在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會記得你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在改變主意還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧 到外面的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就…
